OL,3,CMan allegedly murdered by his wife had
OL,4,C'threatened to shoot neighbours' dog'
OL,6,FA motor racing champion who was
OL,7,Fallegedly murdered by his wife
OL,8,Ffrequently argued with with neighbours
OL,9,Fand once threatened to shoot their
OL,10,Fdog, a court has heard.
OL,12,FIan Rawle, 70, died from a stab wound
OL,13,Fat the home he shared with Christine
OL,14,FRawle in north Devon in 2022.
OL,16,Fat Exeter Crown Court.
OL,18,FJurors heard evidence from Rebecca and
OL,19,FJonathan Squire, who lived close to
OL,20,Fthe Rawles in Kittiwell Wood, near
OL,21,FBraunton, with their young children.
