OL,3,CMan allegedly murdered by his wife had
OL,4,C'threatened to shoot neighbours' dog'
OL,6,F"I didn't know if I had annoyed him,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "He could sometimes be
OL,8,Fconfrontational."
OL,10,FThe court heard Mr Rawle followed Mrs
OL,11,FSquire into a branch of Tesco and she
OL,12,Fwas left feeling uncomfortable.
OL,14,F"Where we live is quite secluded, so
OL,15,Fit's not nice feeling like you're on
OL,16,Fyour own," she said.
OL,18,F"I would make a conscious effort to
OL,19,Fkeep out of his way."
