OL,3,CMan allegedly murdered by his wife had
OL,4,C'threatened to shoot neighbours' dog'
OL,6,FJonathan Squire told the court he was
OL,7,Fonce confronted by Mr Rawle over a
OL,8,Fretaining wall.
OL,10,F"He was aggressive from the get-go,"
OL,11,FMr Squire said.
OL,13,FThe court heard Mr Rawle threatened to
OL,14,Fshoot one of Mr and Mrs Squire's dogs.
OL,16,F"They used to have chickens," Mr
OL,17,FSquire told the court. "He said if
OL,18,Fthey keep upsetting the chickens, I
OL,19,Fwill shoot the dog."
