OL,3,CMan allegedly murdered by his wife had
OL,4,C'threatened to shoot neighbours' dog'
OL,6,FThe court heard Mrs Rawle would
OL,7,Ffrequently refer to her husband as
OL,8,F'd***khead'.JEquine dentist Peter Nott
OL,9,Fgave evidence and was asked about his
OL,10,Ffriendship with Ian Rawle and his
OL,11,Fopinion of the couple's relationship.
OL,12,F"To call your husband d***head in
OL,13,Fpublic is not a nice thing to do," Mr
OL,14,FNott said.J"I used to hear d*** and
OL,15,Fd***head time and time again."
OL,17,FChristine Rawle denies murder. The
OL,18,Ftrial continues.
